The hall with 6 court is a popular place that can be used for many different activities like badminton, netball etc. Corporste event cam be held there too. They swimming pool and track and field. This place is accessible by wheelchair too.
Finally the a sport shop and a fast food restaurant too.', 'languageCode': 'en'}
